                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090920-131-defend1314 t18090920-131-punish772"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Justice Bailey.</p>
